{
  "stem": "13874.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He later developed epilepsy, and sooner or later, he-- he got more and more-- was more and more affected by it and afflicted by it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he died from it in 1932.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It's-- when we-- when Hitler came to power, it was a shock.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remember one thing very vividly, going to school, and I was told I had to sit in the back of the class.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "was in 1933, after Hitler got to power.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And during the last year, I was sitting in the back of the class.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The teachers didn't talk to me too much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some were indirectly sympathetic, but that was life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I was 16, I was told frankly, you had all your legal education.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I had to become a-- I had to learn a trade for immigration.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know-- being a businessman is no-- nothing to immigrate with, so I wanted-- also [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all those machine shops and all the factories, they were taken over by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So only thing I really could become was a tailor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so finally, I was apprenticed to a little tailor in Wurzburg.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was my trade.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I started out when I was 16.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was in 1936.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody talked to me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were afraid to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a business that suddenly came to a standstill.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we just were outcast.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we never thought ourselves anything different than German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That really came as a shock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe I-- if I-- in Poland for instance, there was-- was always quite a bit of anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Jews were Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And considered a nationality, Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Our nationality was German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Period.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've said enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
